Regular Method: In large microwaveable bowl, microwave margarine at HIGH about 1 minute or until melted. Stir in sugar, dates, cherries and egg; mix well. Microwave at HIGH 4 - 42 minutes, stirring every 12 minutes, until mixture is smooth and thickened. Add vanilla. Stir in cereal and nuts; mix well. Drop by 15 mL (tablespoon) measure onto coconut in shallow dish. Form into balls, rolling in coconut. Chill. Store in refrigerator, covered.